Class 41 27/11/2025

Real time things
================
1) consultency : a physically located company along with documents (Offer Letter, Last hike letter, last 3 monthes pay slips and while leaving they will provide releaving letter)
2) shift pattren : 2 shifts, 6:30 to 3:30 PM, 1:30 to 10:30 PM Night shift will be supported by US team
3) role Changes for a week, Proceess Implementation Document(PID). Normal change, emergency change, standard changes
	a) new configuration setup
	b) modification of the current configuration
4) role Incidents for a week, priority1, p2, p3, p4
	a) service down alert
	b) server down alert
	c) file system curreption
	d) hardware failures
5) Environment Used Tools:
	Monitoring tool: Nagios, IMON
	Ticketing tool: e-tracker
	Messaging tool: MS teams
	Email : MS Outlook
	password manager: all server root passowrds will be stored
6) Escalation Matrics:
	First point of contact : Lead 
	Next point of contact : Manager
	Next point of contact : Delivery Manager
	Then point of contact is : Communication Officer
7) DataCenters: Texas in US, Hazalwood in UK, Ctrls-Hyd/India
8) Roles/Responsibulities: 
	a) what are the skills you have
	b) how many servers you are supporting (1500+)
	c) daily activity process
	d) work style
9) L1/L2/L3 support management
